106
00:10:22,654 --> 00:10:26,283
and look really hard inside myself
for what I really want.

107
00:10:29,728 --> 00:10:33,528
Claire, you're obviously frightened
by taking this test. Why?

108
00:10:36,701 --> 00:10:38,168
I don't know.

109
00:10:39,337 --> 00:10:42,135
It's like, when I think about the test...

110
00:10:42,574 --> 00:10:45,202
