for a long time...

121
00:11:27,085 --> 00:11:31,021
and somebody moves in
and renovates the house across the street...

122
00:11:31,089 --> 00:11:34,422
that could just make you feel
your own house is shabby.

123
00:11:34,492 --> 00:11:35,652
I see.

124
00:11:36,227 --> 00:11:38,661
- Did you just insult me?
- Of course not.

125
00:11:39,631 --> 00:11:40,996
