126
00:11:41,299 --> 00:11:44,200
When you're ready,
you're going to live in a palace.

127
00:11:44,469 --> 00:11:46,596
Claire, wash your hands. We're about to eat.

128
00:11:46,671 --> 00:11:49,162
Don't set a place for me. I'm not staying.

129
00:11:49,874 --> 00:11:52,240
