Okay, I have a date.

134
00:12:05,090 --> 00:12:08,526
David, I'm having a problem
with the Emily Previn funeral.

135
00:12:08,593 --> 00:12:10,083
Let's hear it.

136
00:12:10,361 --> 00:12:15,321
I've called her entire contact list, and
the friends she listed have moved or died.

137
00:12:15,433 --> 00:12:17,025
She has two distant relatives.

138
00:12:17,102 --> 00:12:20,833
