I could defend people who are guilty.

175
00:14:15,920 --> 00:14:19,083
I guess I could be
a some-of-the-public defender.

176
00:14:21,159 --> 00:14:23,059
So, what do you do?

177
00:14:23,561 --> 00:14:28,021
Me? My family owns a business.
Actually, it's a funeral home.

178
00:14:31,436 --> 00:14:34,837
But I got out of that really quickly,
and now I'm in textiles.

179
00:14:36,341 --> 00:14:37,831
I like fabric.

180
00:14:39,677 --> 00:14:42,976
