I have a lot of work...

181
00:14:43,047 --> 00:14:46,813
- Okay. Maybe we'll see each other around.
- David, relax.

182
00:14:46,885 --> 00:14:50,946
It's fine. I understand.
I guess there's not much of a spark here.

183
00:14:51,522 --> 00:14:53,820
I thought there was. You don't?

184
00:14:54,225 --> 00:14:57,558
No, I do. I was just worried.

185
00:14:59,097 --> 00:15:01,657
I'm sorry, Ben.
I get a little nervous at these things.

186
00:15:01,733 --> 00:15:04,725
If I seem calm,
it's only because I take a beta-blocker...

187
00:15:04,802 --> 00:15:09,205
before I have to get in front of a jury
or first dates.

188
00:15:09,707 --> 00:15:13,803
