been in Oakland so long?

211
00:16:37,862 --> 00:16:38,886
No.

212
00:16:39,130 --> 00:16:42,327
Okay. But we don't know how long
you're gonna be here.

213
00:16:42,400 --> 00:16:46,632
So why don't we both try
and ease up on each other a little bit, okay?

214
00:16:47,405 --> 00:16:49,600
You guys have bad toothpaste.

215
00:16:50,775 --> 00:16:55,735
My first instinct is to get angry with her.
I open my mouth, I hear my father.

216
00:16:57,515 --> 00:17:01,144
Stop being so hard on yourself.
That child is not easy.

217
00:17:02,186 --> 00:17:05,121
I swore to myself I would never be like him.

218
00:17:11,195 --> 00:17:12,924
I'm not in the mood.

219
00:17:17,368 --> 00:17:18,460
Fine.

220
00:18:06,584 --> 00:18:07,778
<i>Get up!</i>

221
00:18:56,901 --> 00:18:59,995
